rows.label: qst000905_msg0001
rows.name:
Thank you so much! I'm
glad Doruru-san is safe.

rows.label: qst000905_msg0002
rows.name:
This incident has made me realize
just how lacking in skill we are.

rows.label: qst000905_msg0003
rows.name:
It's pathetic, but it seems
this job was too much for us.

rows.label: qst000905_msg0004
rows.name:
If we're struggling with Ignas,
becoming the strongest mercenary
band is just a pipe dream...

rows.label: qst000905_msg0005
rows.name: But something good came out of it!

rows.label: qst000905_msg0006
rows.name:
Doruru-san said he'll invest
in our mercenary band!

rows.label: qst000905_msg0007
rows.name:
We'll do our best to live
up to his expectations!

rows.label: qst000905_msg0009
rows.name:
This is the reward from Doruru-san
for this job. But we don't have
the right to accept it now.

rows.label: qst000905_msg0012
rows.name:
We'll learn from this
experience and become stronger,
so we won't lose to you!
